<p>The reimbursements mailbox poll job can't authenticate against Microsoft Graph.</p>
<p><strong>Detail:</strong> <%= @detail %></p>
<p>
  Most likely the Entra client secret has expired or been revoked. Receipt emails are
  <strong>not</strong> being processed until this is fixed (they stay unread and will be
  picked up once authentication works again).
</p>
<p>
  Rotate the secret: entra.microsoft.com → App registrations →
  "BlackLightning Reimbursements Mailbox" → Certificates &amp; secrets, then update the
  Rails production credentials and redeploy.
</p>
<p>This alert is sent at most once per day.</p>
